            . I am the mother of the prisoner; I never knew any thing had of him;<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177405180005"></xptr> he was apprentice to a <rs id="t17740518-2-deflabel10" type="occupation">shagreen case maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740518-2-defend68 t17740518-2-deflabel10"></join>; he had served four years; his master failed; he has worked journey work since; I took a deal of pains with him and gave him a good education.</p>
